            <t:note>Preliminary division into textparts based on     <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/NIG5B4QK"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1927Inediti"/><title level="a">Di alcuni scritti etiopici inediti</title><title level="j">Rendiconti della R. Accademia nazionale dei Lincei, Classe di scienze morali, storiche e filologiche</title><author><forename>Carlo</forename><surname>Conti Rossini</surname></author><date>1927</date><biblScope unit="volume">Serie sesta, 3</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">7-10</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">497-528</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">Ethiopic script</note><note type="tag">Hagiography</note><note type="tag">bm:ContiRossini1927Inediti</note><note type="tag">Egziabher nags</note><note type="tag">Marqoryos</note><note type="tag">Nagara liqawent</note></note><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">Ethiopic script</note><note type="tag">Hagiography</note><note type="tag">bm:ContiRossini1927Inediti</note><note type="tag">Egziabher nags</note><note type="tag">Marqoryos</note><note type="tag">Nagara liqawent</note><t:citedRange unit="page">500-511</t:citedRange></t:bibl> and <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient641">London, British Library, BL Oriental 641</t:ref>. The text is taken from <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/NIG5B4QK"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1927Inediti"/><title level="a">Di alcuni scritti etiopici inediti</title><title level="j">Rendiconti della R. Accademia nazionale dei Lincei, Classe di scienze morali, storiche e filologiche</title><author><forename>Carlo</forename><surname>Conti Rossini</surname></author><date>1927</date><biblScope unit="volume">Serie sesta, 3</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">7-10</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">497-528</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">Ethiopic script</note><note type="tag">Hagiography</note><note type="tag">bm:ContiRossini1927Inediti</note><note type="tag">Egziabher nags</note><note type="tag">Marqoryos</note><note type="tag">Nagara liqawent</note></note><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">Ethiopic script</note><note type="tag">Hagiography</note><note type="tag">bm:ContiRossini1927Inediti</note><note type="tag">Egziabher nags</note><note type="tag">Marqoryos</note><note type="tag">Nagara liqawent</note><t:citedRange unit="page">500-511</t:citedRange></t:bibl>.</t:note>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="title">
               <t:label>Title</t:label>
               <t:ab>በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ገድል፡ ወስምዕ፡ ዘብፁዕ፡ ወቅዱስ፡ ስብስትያኖስ፡ ዘፈጸመ፡ ገድሎ፡ አመ፡ ፳ወ<t:supplied resp="DR" reason="undefined">፭</t:supplied>፡ ለወርኀ፡ ጥር።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="supplicationBeginning" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="supplicationBeginning">
               <t:label>Supplication</t:label>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" subtype="mainText">
               <t:label>Main Text</t:label>
               
               <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" subtype="incipit" xml:id="incipit">
                  <t:label>Incipit</t:label>
                  <t:ab>ወኮነ፡ ልደቱ፡ ለዝንቱ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በሀገረ፡ ናርቦና፡ ዘእም<choice resp="DR">
                        <t:sic>ህ</t:sic>
                        <t:corr>ሀ</t:corr>
                     </choice>ገር፡ እምርት፡ እምአድባር፡ ኢጣርያ፡ ወተምህረ፡ መጻሕፍተ፡ በሀገረ፡ ሚላኖ።</t:ab>
               </t:div>
               
               <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" subtype="explicit" xml:id="explicit">
                  <t:label>Explicit</t:label>
                  <t:ab>ወኮነ፡ ዕረፍቱ፡ አመ፳ወ፭፡ ለወርኃ፡ ጥር፡ ወሎቱ፡ ያብዕሉ፡ በሀገረ፡ ሮሜ፡ ሰብእ፡ መሃይምናን፡ በፍሥሐ፡ ወበሐሤት፡ ወአዕርጎ፡ መሥዋዕት፡ ወበምሂረ፡ ነዳያን፡ እንዘ፡ ይትአመኑ፡ በጸሎቱ፡ ማሕያዊት፡ </t:ab>
               </t:div>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" subtype="doxology" xml:id="doxology">
               <t:label>Doxology</t:label>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" subtype="supplicationEnd" xml:id="supplicationEnd">
               <t:label>Supplication</t:label>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" subtype="salam" xml:id="salam">
               <t:label>Salām</t:label>
               <t:note>Text taken from <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient641">London, British Library, BL Oriental 641</t:ref>.</t:note>
               <t:ab>ሰላም፡ ለርእስከ፡ እንተ፡ በዲቤሁ፡ ልኩዕ፨ አክሊለ፡ ሞገስ፡ ወግርማ። ወጌራ፡ መዊእ፨ ስብስትያኖስ፡ ብፁዕ፡ ሰማዕተ፡ እግዚእ፨ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በስቃይከ፡ ወረድኤትከ፡ ባቍዕ፨ ኅብአኒ፡ እምብድብድ፡ ወደዌ፡ ካልእ፨</t:ab>
            </t:div>
         </t:div>
      </t:body>
